{"tid":2405971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於bee.com我可能炒左車","createTime":"2021-02-12T21:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T08:20:03.000Z","uid":335303,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"115448c189daa7d4a9382a947b00de970c1b439b","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:15:13.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">雖然我個名叫<del>打手</del>,<a href=\"http://但我一直都屌緊bee.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%86%E6%88%91%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%83%BD%E5%B1%8C%E7%B7%8Abee.com&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=5e1b5472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">但我一直都屌緊bee.com</a></p><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fy5oVu0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffy5oVu0.jpg&h=d8950629&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTW3Vu4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTW3Vu4.jpg&h=834f7f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但呢個，我可能真係<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">炒左車</span></span></strong><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"http://首先我地對bee.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E6%88%91%E5%9C%B0%E5%B0%8Dbee.com&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=8c291f6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">首先我地對bee.com</a>最大嘅指控係<span class=\"red\">支那野</span><br />\n而我地嘅證據，只係得<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"medium\">支那ICP備案</span></strong></span>，係支那美圖備嘅</p><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vjMTgV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vjMTgV.jpg&h=8e224cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<p class=\"center\">佢嘅審核時間係2020-6-30<br />\n呢個信息最後更新嘅日期係2020-12-29<br />\n<a href=\"http://而bee.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%80%8Cbee.com&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=64994664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">而bee.com</a>開始嘅時間係2020-12-3</p><br />\n<a href=\"http://我好自然會覺得bee.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E5%A5%BD%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9C%83%E8%A6%BA%E5%BE%97bee.com&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=ad4b8005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我好自然會覺得bee.com</a>就係美圖期下嘅產物<br />\n<br />\n但係，如果美圖呢間公司<span class=\"red\">賣左個網址</span>，<span class=\"red\">而冇注銷備案</span>，加上中國個icp系統係廢嫁呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><a href=\"http://咁bee.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%92%81bee.com&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=0278415b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">咁bee.com</a> 喺icp系統入面就會係美圖嘅網站</span></span></p></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7o9Q4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7o9Q4j.jpg&h=cdd70011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBmb4pk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBmb4pk.jpg&h=f5d90f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度可以睇到會同一日更新備案，同一日注銷<br />\n可以推斷，如果6月30日未知會賣，美圖就會備案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5ZhfvT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5ZhfvT.jpg&h=723d0525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度睇到佢SSL證書真係轉左<code>唔肯定關唔關事</code><br />\n個時間都吻合<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRVL8Re.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRVL8Re.jpg&h=7f347b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://呢個係以前美圖嘅bee.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E4%BF%82%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%96%E5%98%85bee.com&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=452230e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">呢個係以前美圖嘅bee.com</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6e40c0eed25ac418c2f2b7377a7af56ace0ca4","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583ddd2f370d1f13f58368b56361542e4a982b57","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:17:48.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"a9fb8864ec6f0d2a183e64d99ed8b2d5c0a6443b","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:17:59.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"e8de7806e3658cda800c5485e2e52d5949818607","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:18:15.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"338ab442b86e05654e62ad26e13d88384281c0da","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:18:25.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"a75a10aa3139d4d3ce688e6837b0edde26af1af4","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:19:41.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"567fe4174be05c9b7745f9786b5c7229942f738a","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:19:57.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"77d5dec25ab3c19dc8b158bace9b6bc248969bf9","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:20:16.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"cd59adf55ad58eb8437c178b99616cd3409d2c99","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:20:27.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"fc1758781a44c4248181e1ece4e01ea8dd78cc4c","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:20:37.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"8647498f49b46c505965c148c7872f228c55dd07","tid":2405971,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T21:20:49.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"d1fb4d8a68cbbfa2003cf54004d826e35239bae8","tid":2405971,"uid":217993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2